pan begin="53.650" end="53.950">背</span><span begin="53.950" end="54.440">骨</span><span begin="54.440" end="54.760">を</span><span begin="54.920" end="55.150">撫</span><span begin="55.150" end="55.450">で</span><span begin="55.630" end="56.310">回</span><span begin="56.310" end="56.450">す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">抚遍我的脊梁</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">撫遍我的脊樑</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Caresse ma colonne vertébrale</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Acaricia mi columna vertebral</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Streichelt meinen Rücken</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Acaricia a minha espinha</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Гладит меня по позвоночнику</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi accarezza la spina dorsale</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sebone o nademawasu</span></p><p begin="57.530" end="1:02.620" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="57.530" end="57.810">ま</span><span begin="57.810" end="58.020">る</span><span begin="58.020" end="58.290">で</span><span begin="58.290" end="58.500">も</span><span begin="58.500" end="58.720">う</span><span begin="59.000" end="59.470">誰</span><span begin="59.470" end="59.700">も</span><span begin="59.700" end="59.950">い</span><span begin="59.950" end="1:00.210">な</span><span begin="1:00.210" end="1:00.530">い</span><span begin="1:00.640" end="1:00.930">か</span><span begin="1:00.930" end="1:01.390">の</span><span begin="1:01.390" end="1:01.510">よ</span><span begin="1:01.510" end="1:01.630">う</span><span begin="1:01.630" end="1:02.620">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">仿佛这世间已空无一人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">彷彿這世間已空無一人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme s&apos;il n&apos;y avait déjà plus personne</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como si ya no quedara nadie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Als ob schon niemand mehr hier wäre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como se não houvesse mais ninguém</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Словно вокруг больше никого нет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Proprio come se non ci fosse più nessuno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Marude mou dare mo inai ka no you ni</span></p><p begin="1:06.660" end="1:12.450" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:06.660" end="1:07.160">上</span><span begin="1:07.160" end="1:07.370">履</span><span begin="1:07.370" end="1:07.630">き</span><span begin="1:07.630" end="1:07.880">で</span><span begin="1:07.880" end="1:08.200">ラ</span><span begin="1:08.200" end="1:08.350">ン</span><span begin="1:08.350" end="1:08.610">デ</span><span begin="1:08.610" end="1:08.820">ヴ</span><span begin="1:09.060" end="1:09.560">同</span><span begin="1:09.560" end="1:10.050">一</span><span begin="1:10.050" end="1:10.230">の</span><span begin="1:10.230" end="1:10.510">軌</span><span begin="1:10.510" end="1:10.980">道</span><span begin="1:10.980" end="1:11.470">上</span><span begin="1:11.470" end="1:12.450">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">穿着室内鞋的幽会 在同一条轨道上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">穿著室內鞋的幽會 在同一條軌道上</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Rendez-vous en chaussures d&apos;école sur la même orbite</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Una cita en zapatos escolares sobre la misma órbita</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Rendezvous in Hausschuhen auf derselben Umlaufbahn</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Encontro de sapatos escolares na mesma órbita</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Рандеву в сменной обуви на одной орбите</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Rendez-vous con le scarpe di scuola sulla stessa orbita</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Uwabaki de randevu douitsu no kidoujou de</span></p><p begin="1:12.880" end="1:17.010" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:12.880" end="1:13.380">君</span><span begin="1:13.380" end="1:13.640">に</span><span begin="1:13.640" end="1:13.910">会</span><span begin="1:13.910" end="1:14.100">え</span><span begin="1:14.100" end="1:14.370">た</span><span begin="1:14.370" end="1:14.600">ら</span><span begin="1:15.070" end="1:15.590">い</span><span begin="1:15.590" end="1:16.440">い</span><span begin="1:16.550" end="1:16.940">の</span><span begin="1:16.940" end="1:17.010">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">若是能见到你就好了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">若是能見到你就好了</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si seulement je pouvais te rencontrer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ojalá pudiera encontrarme contigo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich wünschte ich könnte dich treffen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Queria poder te encontrar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ах если бы я могла встретить тебя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Magari potessi incontrarti</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi ni aetara ii noni</span></p><p begin="1:32.330" end="1:34.420" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:32.330" end="1:32.800">お</span><span begin="1:32.800" end="1:33.070">し</span><span begin="1:33.070" end="1:33.210">え</span><span begin="1:33.320" end="1:33.570">て</span><span begin="1:33.570" end="1:33.760">お</span><span begin="1:33.760" end="1:34.020">し</span><span begin="1:34.020" end="1:34.150">え</span><span begin="1:34.270" end="1:34.420">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">告诉我吧 告诉我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">告訴我吧 告訴我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dis-moi dis-moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dime dime</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sag mir sag mir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Me diga me diga</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Скажи мне скажи мне</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dimmi dimmi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Oshiete oshiete</span></p><p begin="1:34.500" end="1:36.720" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:34.500" end="1:34.750">か</span><span begin="1:34.750" end="1:34.940">み</span><span begin="1:34.940" end="1:35.220">さ</span><span begin="1:35.220" end="1:35.480">ま</span><span begin="1:35.480" end="1:35.710">は</span><span begin="1:35.710" end="1:35.990">ど</span><span begin="1:35.990" end="1:36.150">う</span><span begin="1:36.150" end="1:36.430">し</span><span begin="1:36.430" end="1:36.720">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">神明大人究竟为何</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">神明大人究竟為何</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dieu pourquoi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dios por qué</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gott warum</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Deus por que</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Почему же бог</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dio perché</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kamisama wa doushite</span></p><p begin="1:36.720" end="1:39.760" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:36.720" end="1:36.790">い</span><span begin="1:36.900" end="1:37.170">つ</span><span begin="1:37.170" end="1:37.510">も</span><span begin="1:37.510" end="1:37.870">迎</span><span begin="1:37.870" end="1:38.120">え</span><span begin="1:38.120" end="1:38.350">を</span><span begin="1:38.350" end="1:38.570">寄</span><span begin="1:38.570" end="1:38.780">越</span><span begin="1:38.780" end="1:39.090">さ</span><span begin="1:39.090" end="1:39.340">な</span><span begin="1:39.340" end="1:39.580">い</span><span begin="1:39.580" end="1:39.760">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">总是未曾以此迎接我呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">總是未曾以此迎接我呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">N&apos;envoies-tu jamais personne me chercher</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nunca envías a nadie a recogerme</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Schickst du nie jemanden der mich abholt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você nunca manda me buscar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Никогда не присылает за мной</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non mandi mai nessuno a prendermi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itsumo mukae o yokosanai no</span></p><p begin="1:40.020" end="1:42.190" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:40.020" end="1:40.460">お</span><span begin="1:40.460" end="1:40.740">し</span><span begin="1:40.740" end="1:40.890">え</span><span begin="1:41.000" end="1:41.260">て</span><span begin="1:41.260" end="1:41.460">お</span><span begin="1:41.460" end="1:41.700">し</span><span begin="1:41.700" end="1:41.840">え</span><span begin="1:41.950" end="1:42.190">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">告诉我吧 告诉我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">告訴我吧 告訴我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dis-moi dis-moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dime dime</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sag mir sag mir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Me diga me diga</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Скажи мне скажи мне</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dimmi dimmi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Oshiete oshiete</span></p><p begin="1:42.190" end="1:44.080" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:42.190" end="1:42.410">あ</span><span begin="1:42.410" end="1:42.570">な</span><span begin="1:42.670" end="1:42.920">た</span><span begin="1:42.920" end="1:43.150">は</span><span begin="1:43.150" end="1:43.420">ど</span><span begin="1:43.420" end="1:43.620">う</span><span begin="1:43.620" end="1:43.870">し</span><span begin="1:43.870" end="1:44.080">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你究竟为何</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你究竟為何</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Toi pourquoi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tú por qué</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Warum kannst du</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Por que você</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Почему же ты</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Tu perché</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anata wa doushite</span></p><p begin="1:44.100" end="1:47.400" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:44.100" end="1:44.370">ま</span><span begin="1:44.370" end="1:44.590">ば</span><span begin="1:44.590" end="1:44.820">た</span><span begin="1:44.820" end="1:45.190">き</span><span begin="1:45.190" end="1:45.310">ひ</span><span begin="1:45.310" end="1:45.540">と</span><span begin="1:45.540" end="1:45.780">つ</span><span begin="1:45.780" end="1:46.020">も</span><span begin="1:46.020" end="1:46.470">許</span><span begin="1:46.470" end="1:46.770">せ</span><span begin="1:46.770" end="1:47.030">な</span><span begin="1:47.030" end="1:47.260">い</span><span begin="1:47.260" end="1:47.400">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">连一次瞬目都无法宽恕呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">連一次瞬目都無法寬恕呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ne pardonnes-tu même pas un battement de cils</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No permites ni un solo parpadeo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Nicht ein einziges Blinzeln verzeihen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não perdoa nem um único piscar de olhos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Не прощаешь даже одного моргания</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non mi perdoni nemmeno un battito di ciglia</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mabataki hitotsu mo yurusenai no</span></p><p begin="1:47.670" end="1:49.780" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:47.670" end="1:48.020">お</span><span begin="1:48.150" end="1:48.450">し</span><span begin="1:48.450" end="1:48.670">え</span><span begin="1:48.670" end="1:48.900">て</span><span begin="1:48.900" end="1:49.100">お</span><span begin="1:49.100" end="1:49.400">し</span><span begin="1:49.400" end="1:49.520">え</span><span begin="1:49.620" end="1:49.780">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">告诉我吧 告诉我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">告訴我吧 告訴我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dis-moi dis-moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dime dime</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sag mir sag mir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Me diga me diga</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Скажи мне скажи мне</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dimmi dimmi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Oshiete oshiete</span></p><p begin="1:49.850" end="1:52.010" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:49.850" end="1:50.130">か</span><span begin="1:50.130" end="1:50.310">み</span><span begin="1:50.310" end="1:50.580">さ</span><span begin="1:50.580" end="1:50.870">ま</span><span begin="1:50.870" end="1:51.060">は</span><span begin="1:51.060" end="1:51.290">ど</span><span begin="1:51.290" end="1:51.430">う</span><span begin="1:51.530" end="1:51.790">し</span><span begin="1:51.790" end="1:52.010">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">神明大人究竟为何</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">神明大人究竟為何</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dieu pourquoi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dios por qué</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gott warum</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Deus por que</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Почему же бог</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dio perché</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kamisama wa doushite</span></p><p begin="1:52.010" end="1:55.060" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:52.010" end="1:52.390">人</span><span begin="1:52.500" end="1:52.790">と</span><span begin="1:52.790" end="1:52.990">お</span><span begin="1:52.990" end="1:53.240">ん</span><span begin="1:53.240" end="1:53.470">な</span><span begin="1:53.470" end="1:53.690">じ</span><span begin="1:53.690" end="1:54.210">顔</span><span begin="1:54.210" end="1:54.400">を</span><span begin="1:54.400" end="1:54.660">す</span><span begin="1:54.660" end="1:54.940">る</span><span begin="1:54.940" end="1:55.060">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">却有着与人一般的面孔呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">卻有著與人一般的面孔呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">As-tu le même visage qu&apos;un humain</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Tienes la misma cara que una persona</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hast du das gleiche Gesicht wie ein Mensch</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você tem o mesmo rosto que as pessoas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">С таким же лицом как у людей</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Hai lo stesso volto delle persone</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hito to onnaji kao o suru no</span></p><p begin="1:55.380" end="1:57.570" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:55.380" end="1:55.850">ご</span><span begin="1:55.850" end="1:56.100">め</span><span begin="1:56.100" end="1:56.380">ん</span><span begin="1:56.380" end="1:56.530">ね</span><span begin="1:56.640" end="1:56.850">ご</span><span begin="1:56.850" end="1:57.070">め</span><span begin="1:57.070" end="1:57.350">ん</span><span begin="1:57.350" end="1:57.570">ね</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">对不起 对不起</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">對不起 對不起</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pardon pardon</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Lo siento lo siento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Tut mir leid tut mir leid</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Desculpe desculpe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Прости меня прости меня</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Scusa scusa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Gomenne gomenne</span></p><p begin="1:57.570" end="1:59.440" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:57.570" end="1:58.030">思</span><span begin="1:58.030" end="1:58.260">い</span><span begin="1:58.260" end="1:58.480">出</span><span begin="1:58.480" end="1:58.750">ひ</span><span begin="1:58.750" end="1:58.990">と</span><span begin="1:58.990" end="1:59.230">つ</span><span begin="1:59.230" end="1:59.440">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">仅凭一段回忆</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">僅憑一段回憶</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Avec un seul souvenir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Con un solo recuerdo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wegen einer einzigen Erinnerung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Com apenas uma lembrança</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Из-за одного лишь воспоминания</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Con un solo ricordo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Omoide hitotsu de</span></p><p begin="1:59.460" end="2:07.200" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:59.460" end="1:59.700">泣</span><span begin="1:59.700" end="1:59.850">け</span><span begin="1:59.960" end="2:00.180">て</span><span begin="2:00.180" end="2:00.540">は</span><span begin="2:00.540" end="2:00.700">い</span><span begin="2:00.700" end="2:00.930">ら</span><span begin="2:00.930" end="2:01.070">れ</span><span begin="2:01.170" end="2:01.410">な</span><span begin="2:01.410" end="2:01.510">い</span><span begin="2:01.660" end="2:02.110">の</span><span begin="2:02.110" end="2:02.360">に</span><span begin="2:02.580" end="2:03.100">爆</span><span begin="2:03.100" end="2:03.550">ぜ</span><span begin="2:03.550" end="2:05.370">そ</span><span begin="2:05.370" end="2:07.200">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">明明已无法哭泣 却感觉身心几欲炸裂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">明明已無法哭泣 卻感覺身心幾欲炸裂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne devrais pas pleurer mais je suis sur le point d&apos;exploser</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No puedo ponerme a llorar pero siento que voy a estallar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Darf ich nicht weinen und doch platze ich fast</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não posso ficar chorando mas sinto que vou explodir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я не должна плакать но я вот-вот взорвусь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non dovrei piangere eppure sto per esplodere</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nakete wa irarenai noni hazesou</span></p><p begin="2:33.810" end="2:35.850" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:33.810" end="2:34.250">お</span><span begin="2:34.250" end="2:34.510">し</span><span begin="2:34.510" end="2:34.650">え</span><span begin="2:34.750" end="2:35.020">て</span><span begin="2:35.020" end="2:35.200">お</span><span begin="2:35.200" end="2:35.480">し</span><span begin="2:35.480" end="2:35.590">え</span><span begin="2:35.700" end="2:35.850">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">告诉我吧 告诉我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">告訴我吧 告訴我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dis-moi dis-moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dime dime</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sag mir sag mir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Me diga me diga</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Скажи мне скажи мне</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dimmi dimmi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Oshiete oshiete</span></p><p begin="2:35.920" end="2:38.130" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:35.920" end="2:36.170">か</span><span begin="2:36.170" end="2:36.370">み</span><span begin="2:36.370" end="2:36.680">さ</span><span begin="2:36.680" end="2:36.960">ま</span><span begin="2:36.960" end="2:37.140">は</span><span begin="2:37.140" end="2:37.400">ど</span><span begin="2:37.400" end="2:37.580">う</span><span begin="2:37.580" end="2:37.770">し</span><span begin="2:37.870" end="2:38.130">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">神明大人究竟为何</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">神明大人究竟為何</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dieu pourquoi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dios por qué</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gott warum</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Deus por que</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Почему же бог</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dio perché</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kamisama wa doushite</span></p><p begin="2:38.130" end="2:41.180" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:38.130" end="2:38.310">い</span><span begin="2:38.310" end="2:38.560">つ</span><span begin="2:38.560" end="2:38.780">も</span><span begin="2:38.780" end="2:39.350">迎</span><span begin="2:39.350" end="2:39.550">え</span><span begin="2:39.550" end="2:39.770">に</span><span begin="2:39.770" end="2:40.030">来</span><span begin="2:40.030" end="2:40.260">ら</span><span begin="2:40.260" end="2:40.540">れ</span><span begin="2:40.540" end="2:40.770">な</span><span begin="2:40.770" end="2:41.020">い</span><span begin="2:41.020" end="2:41.180">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">总是无法前来迎接呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">總是無法前來迎接呢</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ne peux-tu jamais venir me chercher</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Nunca puedes venir a recogerme</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Kannst du mich nie abholen kommen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você nunca pode vir me buscar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Никогда не может прийти за мной</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non puoi mai venire a prendermi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itsumo mukae ni korarenai no</span></p><p begin="2:41.440" end="2:47.510" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:41.440" end="2:41.970">か</span><span begin="2:41.970" end="2:42.140">み</span><span begin="2:42.140" end="2:42.350">さ</span><span begin="2:42.460" end="2:42.710">ま</span><span begin="2:42.710" end="2:42.880">お</span><span begin="2:42.880" end="2:43.140">し</span><span begin="2:43.140" end="2:43.290">え</span><span begin="2:43.400" end="2:43.600">て</span><span begin="2:43.600" end="2:44.130">百</span><span begin="2:44.130" end="2:44.620">年</span><span begin="2:44.620" end="2:44.840">後</span><span begin="2:44.840" end="2:45.030">の</span><span begin="2:45.030" end="2:45.570">花</span><span begin="2:45.570" end="2:47.510">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">神明啊请告诉我 那百年后的花儿</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">神明啊請告訴我 那百年後的花兒</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dieu dis-moi pour la fleur de dans cent ans</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dios dime que las flores de dentro de cien años</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gott sag mir lass die Blumen in hundert Jahren</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Deus me diga faça as flores de cem anos depois</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Боже скажи мне и цветок спустя сто лет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dio dimmi i fiori di tra cent&apos;anni</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kamisama oshiete hyakunengo no hana o</span></p><p begin="2:48.140" end="2:52.450" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:48.140" end="2:48.650">咲</span><span begin="2:48.650" end="2:49.110">か</span><span begin="2:49.110" end="2:49.620">せ</span><span begin="2:49.620" end="2:52.450">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">请让它绽放吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">請讓它綻放吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Fais-la éclore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las harás florecer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Erblühen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Florescerem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Заставь расцвести</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Falli sbocciare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sakasete</span></p><p begin="3:04.700" end="3:06.230" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:04.700" end="3:04.850">聞</span><span begin="3:04.990" end="3:05.260">か</span><span begin="3:05.440" end="3:05.730">せ</span><span begin="3:05.930" end="3:06.230">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">让我听听</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">讓我聽聽</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Fais-moi entendre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Déjame escuchar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass mich hören</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Me deixe ouvir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Дай мне услышать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Fammi sentire</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kikasete</span></p><p begin="3:08.570" end="3:10.060" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:08.570" end="3:08.850">聞</span><span begin="3:08.850" end="3:09.110">か</span><span begin="3:09.280" end="3:09.570">せ</span><span begin="3:09.790" end="3:10.060">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">让我听听</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">讓我聽聽</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Fais-moi entendre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Déjame escuchar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass mich hören</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Me deixe ouvir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Дай мне услышать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Fammi sentire</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kikasete</span></p><p begin="3:12.420" end="3:13.900" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:12.420" end="3:12.640">お</span><span begin="3:12.640" end="3:12.940">し</span><span begin="3:13.150" end="3:13.420">え</span><span begin="3:13.630" end="3:13.900">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">告诉我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">告訴我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dis-moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dime</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sag mir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Me diga</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Скажи мне</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dimmi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Oshiete</span></p><p begin="3:16.270" end="3:17.720" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:16.270" end="3:16.490">お</span><span begin="3:16.490" end="3:16.750">し</span><span begin="3:16.990" end="3:17.260">え</span><span begin="3:17.460" end="3:17.720">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">告诉我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">告訴我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dis-moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dime</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sag mir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Me diga</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Скажи мне</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dimmi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Oshiete</span></p><p begin="3:28.710" end="3:30.980" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:28.710" end="3:29.250">夕</span><span begin="3:29.250" end="3:29.490">暮</span><span begin="3:29.490" end="3:29.730">れ</span><span begin="3:29.730" end="3:29.930">の</span><span begin="3:29.930" end="3:30.070">チ</span><span begin="3:30.070" end="3:30.220">ャ</span><span begin="3:30.220" end="3:30.460">イ</span><span begin="3:30.460" end="3:30.710">ム</span><span begin="3:30.710" end="3:30.980">が</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">黄昏时的钟声</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">黃昏時的鐘聲</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Le carillon du crépuscule</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La campana del atardecer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das Läuten in der Abenddämmerung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O sinal do entardecer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Вечерний звонок</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La campanella del tramonto</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yuugure no chaimu ga</span></p><p begin="3:31.160" end="3:33.960" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:31.160" end="3:31.630">今</span><span begin="3:31.630" end="3:31.880">で</span><span begin="3:31.880" end="3:32.180">も</span><span begin="3:32.370" end="3:32.600">鳴</span><span begin="3:32.600" end="3:32.900">り</span><span begin="3:33.000" end="3:33.800">響</span><span begin="3:33.910" end="3:33.960">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">如今依然回响</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">如今依然迴響</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Résonne encore maintenant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aún resuena ahora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hallt auch jetzt noch wider</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ainda ressoa agora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Всё ещё звучит и сейчас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Risuona ancora adesso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ima demo narihibiku</span></p><p begin="3:34.980" end="3:40.040" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:34.980" end="3:35.470">誰</span><span begin="3:35.470" end="3:35.720">に</span><span begin="3:35.720" end="3:36.030">も</span><span begin="3:36.420" end="3:36.670">ば</span><span begin="3:36.670" end="3:36.890">れ</span><span begin="3:36.890" end="3:37.020">ち</span><span begin="3:37.020" end="3:37.160">ゃ</span><span begin="3:37.160" end="3:37.350">い</span><span begin="3:37.350" end="3:37.650">け</span><span begin="3:37.650" end="3:37.820">な</span><span begin="3:37.820" end="3:38.100">い</span><span begin="3:38.100" end="3:38.360">と</span><span begin="3:38.360" end="3:38.810">こ</span><span begin="3:38.810" end="3:39.060">ろ</span><span begin="3:39.060" end="3:40.040">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在绝不能被任何人发现的地方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在絕不能被任何人發現的地方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dans un endroit où personne ne doit le découvrir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En un lugar donde nadie debe descubrirnos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">An einem Ort wo es niemand erfahren darf</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Em um lugar onde ninguém pode descobrir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Там где никто не должен узнать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In un posto dove nessuno deve scoprirci</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dare ni mo barecha ikenai tokoro de</span></p><p begin="3:44.070" end="3:50.700" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:44.070" end="3:44.330">真</span><span begin="3:44.330" end="3:44.510">っ</span><span begin="3:44.510" end="3:44.820">直</span><span begin="3:44.820" end="3:45.070">ぐ</span><span begin="3:45.070" end="3:45.270">に</span><span begin="3:45.270" end="3:45.770">線</span><span begin="3:45.770" end="3:46.030">路</span><span begin="3:46.030" end="3:46.260">を</span><span begin="3:46.520" end="3:46.980">歩</span><span begin="3:46.980" end="3:47.130">い</span><span begin="3:47.230" end="3:47.720">て</span><span begin="3:47.720" end="3:47.950">み</span><span begin="3:47.950" end="3:48.200">た</span><span begin="3:48.200" end="3:48.430">い</span><span begin="3:48.430" end="3:48.720">な</span><span begin="3:48.720" end="3:48.910">ん</span><span begin="3:48.910" end="3:50.700">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">想要试着在铁轨上径直前行这种话</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">想要試著在鐵軌上徑直前行這種話</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Vouloir marcher tout droit sur les rails</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Eso de querer caminar recto por las vías del tren</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass ich einfach mal geradeaus auf den Gleisen laufen möchte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que eu quero tentar andar direto pelos trilhos do trem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">О том что я хочу пройтись прямо по рельсам</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voler provare a camminare dritto sui binari</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Massugu ni senro o aruite mitai nante</span></p><p begin="3:52.230" end="4:00.340" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:52.230" end="3:52.760">君</span><span begin="3:52.760" end="3:53.000">が</span><span begin="3:53.000" end="3:53.190">聞</span><span begin="3:53.190" end="3:53.480">い</span><span begin="3:53.480" end="3:53.740">た</span><span begin="3:53.740" end="3:54.000">ら</span><span begin="3:54.410" end="3:55.530">笑</span><span begin="3:55.530" end="3:55.900">う</span><span begin="3:55.900" end="3:56.200">だ</span><span begin="3:56.200" end="3:56.670">ろ</span><span begin="3:56.670" end="3:57.140">う</span><span begin="3:57.820" end="4:00.310">か</span><span begin="4:00.310" end="4:00.340">？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">若是被你听见 你会笑话我吗？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">若是被你聽見 你會笑話我嗎？</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Rirais-tu si tu entendais ça ?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">¿Te reirías si lo escucharas?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Würdest du lachen wenn du das hörst?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se você ouvisse isso você riria?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если бы ты услышал ты бы рассмеялся?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Se tu lo sentissi rideresti?</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kimi ga kiitara warau darou ka?</span></p></div></body></tt>